layout.p:
Columns: 225;
                                                  ruled lines: 51;
                                                  written lines: 51; Uniform layout. Ruling by hard point.Visible pricking and stiching. 224 columns in total, one to six columns per membrane. Majuscular and minuscular letter in several places. Special shape of the letter פ occurs frequently. The "puncta extraordinaria" placed on the words fixed by masorah. In most of the fragmetns the end of a verse and of a half-verse marked by a dry-point. An upper dry point sometimes distinguishes between כל, את, הוא and כל-, את-, הוא-.
